title: Biggest Position Battles
itunes:title: Biggest Position Battles
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and NFL Now's Colleen Wolfe -- discuss the latest NFL news including reported interest in Reggie Wayne (4:11) and reaction to Khalil Mack topping the "Making the Leap" list (14:00). The heroes then discuss the eight most intriguing camp battles heading into the season (19:25).
